  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomCertExtensionMBean
    JavaServer Faces Managed Bean for managing the configuration of a single CustomCertificateExtension
    EjbcaJSFHelper
    Class used to integrate the old jsp framework with the new JSF one.
    EjbcaJSFImageResource
    Class used to retrieve EJBCA image resources in JSF views Implements a Map used for retrieving resources.
    EjbcaJSFLanguageResource
    Class used to retrieve EJBCA language resources in JSF views Implements a Map used for retrieving resources.
    EjbcaWebBean
    The main bean for the web interface, it contains all basic functions.
    LanguageProperties
    Properties bag that handles "double type encoding".
    ScepConfigMBean
    JavaServer Faces Managed Bean for managing SCEP configuration.
    SortableSelectItem
    An extension to the SelectItem class that is sortable, used by select lists that should be alphabetic order.
    SystemConfigMBean
    Backing bean for the various system configuration pages.
    SystemConfigurationCtLogManager
    This class is used to manage CT logs in EJBCA's system configuration.
    ValidatorSettings
    This class is responsible for managing the configuration shown under the "Validators" tab in System Configuration.
    WebLanguages
    An class interpreting the language properties files.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AdminDoesntExistException
    An exception thown when trying to change or remove a user that does not exist in the database.
    AdminExistsException
    An exception thown when trying to add a user to the database that already exists.
    CacheClearException
    Thrown as a result of clearing the caches from the UI failing.
    InvalidCustomExtensionPropertyException
    Thrown to indicate that a custom extension property value is invalid.
